node.text: - It’s been an intense 2 wks.. I really appreciate the outpouring of love and support towards me and my family in this time of loss of my sweet brother Harry…  I am reposting my comedy reel for @bhjpoetry and for y’all to bring back a lil smile to y’alls faces.  Have a wonderful Thursday!🥰
@minervavier Cheers, Min )) I've experienced loss, it's terrible, the worst, If we can offer humanity to you despite never meeting then that's a good thing. x
You're great, funny, and so cute ❤️ Awesome 🤗🤗🤗🌷
Awww truly love this clip 🤣🤣🤣. Your truly the queen of comedy 👸👸. @minervavier
😂😂 where can I watch this comedy??
Sorry. I have been off here for a bit. Condolences
It’s a tiny piece, but your work is so good. I might’ve watched more than once...🤓
Im so sorry to hear of your loss 😔
